      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCa0952ab8251710058fa78beb784d42d2"></a>Refitting the timing layshaft pulley
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e12619"> </a>To fit the snap ring (7) in the timing layshaft seat, use the tool no. <span class="bold">88713.2834</span>.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_060703087.jpg"></center>
      </div>
