      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e12629"> </a>Install the inner spacer (6) on the timing layshaft, taking care to align the notch in the spacer with the slot in the key.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_060803088.jpg"></center>
